elements.name: COVIDcode Study Provider Enrollment Questionnaire Submission Group 1 User

steps.name: a COVIDcode Study Provider user has logged in to the COVIDcode Study application
the COVIDcode Study Provider fills out an Enrollment Questionnaire for a "Group 1" who says "Yes" to join the study
enters users full name, required information, and demographics information
does not enter Disease Course and Exposures and Risk Factors information
the enrollment questionnaire should be successfully submitted
